  "text": "A very principle solution of the problem had been suggested in ref. [CITATION_1] . By abandoning periodic boundary conditions in one of the directions in favour of open ones, barriers between the topological sectors are abolished. This idea should work independently of the algorithm that is used in the simulation. The proposal has been further tested [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] and adopted in large scale simulations of lattice QCD with dynamical fermions, see for example refs. [CITATION_4] [CITATION_5] .",
